const roles = ["Радіаційний онколог", "Медичний фізик (інженер-радіолог)", "Медична сестра", "Старша медична сестра", "Інженер-програміст"];
---

<Layout title="Наші фахівці" hideSubNav={true}>
  <main class="relative min-h-screen w-full flex flex-col font-['Bricolage_Grotesque_Variable'] bg-slate-50 overflow-x-hidden pt-8 pb-20">

    <div class="relative z-20 px-6 md:px-12 flex justify-between items-center">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-blue-700 transition-all group">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-blue-600 group-hover:bg-blue-50 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all">
          <Icon name="bx:left-arrow-alt" class="w-6 h-6 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform text-slate-600" />
        </div>
        <span class="hidden sm:block text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">На головну</span>
      </a>

      <button id="toggleFilters" class="md:hidden w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl active:scale-90 transition-all">
        <Icon name="bx:search" class="w-6 h-6" />
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-6 mb-4 px-4">
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(2.2rem,4vh,5rem)] font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tighter uppercase italic leading-none">
        Наша команда
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[9px] mt-2 opacity-60">
        Відділення променевої терапії
      </p>
    </div>

    <div id="filterPanel" class="hidden md:block relative z-30 max-w-[1400px] mx-auto w-full px-6 md:px-24 mb-6 transition-all duration-500">
      <div class="bg-white p-5 md:p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
        
        <div class="flex-[1.5] relative">
          <Icon name="bx:search" class="absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400 w-5 h-5" />
          <input 
            type="text" 
            id="nameSearch" 
            placeholder="Введіть ПІБ..." 
            class="w-full pl-12 pr-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border-none rounded-2xl text-sm font-bold focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600 transition-all outline-none"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1">
          <select id="deptFilter" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border-none rounded-2xl text-sm font-bold focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600 transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer appearance-none">
            <option value="">Усі відділення</option>
            {departments.map(dept => <option value={dept}>{dept}</option>)}
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1">
          <select id="roleFilter" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border-none rounded-2xl text-sm font-bold focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600 transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer appearance-none">
            <option value="">Усі посади</option>
            {roles.map(role => <option value={role}>{role}</option>)}
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center relative z-10 w-full px-4 md:px-16 lg:px-24 xl:px-32 py-4">
      <div class="relative w-full max-w-[1700px]">
        
        <div class="swiper main-swiper w-full overflow-hidden perspective">
          <div class="swiper-wrapper" id="doctorsWrapper">
            </div>
          
          <div id="noResults" class="hidden text-center py-24">
            <Icon name="bx:info-circle" class="w-16 h-16 text-slate-200 mx-auto mb-4" />
            <p class="text-slate-400 font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Спеціалістів не знайдено</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="swiper-button-prev custom-nav-btn lg:flex"></button>
        <button class="swiper-button-next custom-nav-btn lg:flex"></button>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  @import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css');

  html, body { overflow-y: auto !important; height: auto !important; min-height: 100vh; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  /* Картка Badoo */
  .doctor-badoo-card {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4.5;
    background: #020617;
    border-radius: 2.2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .doctor-badoo-card { border-radius: 1.5rem; aspect-ratio: 10/16; }
  }

  .card-image-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 1; }
  .doctor-img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 1.2s ease; }
  .image-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.98) 0%, rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.4) 30%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .card-summary { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 10; transition: all 0.5s ease; text-align: left; }
  .role-pill { display: inline-block; padding: 0.4rem 1.1rem; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 900; color: white; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .name-text { font-weight: 900; color: white; line-height: 0.85; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -0.05em; text-align: left; }

  .tap-hint { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1.8rem; font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

  .card-details { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 20; background: white; transform: translateY(100%); transition: transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end; }
  .doctor-badoo-card.is-expanded .card-details { transform: translateY(0); }
  .doctor-badoo-card.is-expanded .card-summary { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }

  .details-content { height: 94%; background: white; border-radius: 3rem 3rem 0 0; }
  .drag-line { width: 50px; height: 5px; background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 10px; margin: 0 auto 1.8rem; }
  .detail-label { display: block; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; text-align: left; }

  /* Навігація стрілок */
  .custom-nav-btn { width: 60px !important; height: 60px !important; background: #020617 !important; color: white !important; border-radius: 12px !important; position: absolute !important; top: 50% !important; transform: translateY(-50%) !important; z-index: 50 !important; display: none; }
  .swiper-button-prev { left: -75px !important; }
  .swiper-button-next { right: -75px !important; }

  @media (min-width: 1280px) { .custom-nav-btn { display: flex !important; } }
  .swiper-slide { padding: 25px 0; }
</style>

<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
<script is:inline define:vars={{ doctors }}>
  let mainSwiper;

  function initSwiper() {
    if (mainSwiper) mainSwiper.destroy(true, true);
    mainSwiper = new Swiper('.main-swiper', {
      slidesPerView: 1.15,
      centeredSlides: true,
      spaceBetween: 20,
      grabCursor: true,
      loop: false,
      navigation: { nextEl: '.swiper-button-next', prevEl: '.swiper-button-prev' },
      breakpoints: {
        768: { slidesPerView: 2, spaceBetween: 30, centeredSlides: false },
        1024: { slidesPerView: 3, spaceBetween: 40, centeredSlides: false },
        1600: { slidesPerView: 4, spaceBetween: 40, centeredSlides: false }
      }
    });
  }

  function renderDoctors(list) {
    const wrapper = document.getElementById('doctorsWrapper');
    const noResults = document.getElementById('noResults');
    if (list.length === 0) { wrapper.innerHTML = ''; noResults.classList.remove('hidden'); return; }
    noResults.classList.add('hidden');
    wrapper.innerHTML = list.map(doc => `
      <div class="swiper-slide h-full">
        <div class="doctor-badoo-card group" onclick="this.classList.toggle('is-expanded')">
          <div class="card-image-bg">
            <img src="${doc.image}" alt="${doc.name}" class="doctor-img" />
            <div class="image-overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-summary p-8 md:p-10">
            <div class="role-pill bg-gradient-to-r ${doc.color}">${doc.role}</div>
            <h3 class="name-text text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vh,3rem)]">${doc.name} <br /> ${doc.surname}</h3>
            <div class="tap-hint"><span>Детальна анкета</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-details">
             <div class="details-content p-8 md:p-10 overflow-y-auto">
                <div class="drag-line"></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-8">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-50 shadow-xl overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
                    <img src="${doc.image}" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase leading-none text-lg">${doc.name} <br/> ${doc.surname}</h4>
                    <span class="text-blue-700 font-extrabold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">${doc.role}</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="bio-text italic text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6 mb-8 leading-relaxed font-medium">"${doc.bio}"</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8 border-y border-slate-100 py-6">
                  <div class="stat-item"><span class="detail-label">Досвід</span><p class="detail-value text-slate-900 text-xl font-black">${doc.experience}</p></div>
                  <div class="stat-item"><span class="detail-label">Освіта</span><p class="detail-value text-slate-800 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase leading-tight">${doc.education}</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-8"><span class="detail-label">Досягнення</span><p class="detail-value text-slate-800 text-xs font-semibold">${doc.achievements}</p></div>
                <div class="specializations mb-10"><span class="detail-label mb-4 block">Ключові напрямки</span><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  ${doc.specializations.map(spec => `<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-lg text-[9px] font-black uppercase">${spec}</span>`).join('')}
                </div></div>
                <button class="w-full py-4 rounded-xl text-white font-black uppercase tracking-widest shadow-2xl bg-gradient-to-r ${doc.color}">Записатися на консультацію</button>
             </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    `).join('');
    initSwiper();
  }

  function handleFilters() {
    const nameVal = document.getElementById('nameSearch').value.trim().toLowerCase();
    const deptVal = document.getElementById('deptFilter').value;
    const roleVal = document.getElementById('roleFilter').value;

    const filtered = doctors.filter(doc => {
      // Фікс пошуку: шукаємо збіг у імені АБО прізвищі
      const matchesName = !nameVal || doc.name.toLowerCase().includes(nameVal) || doc.surname.toLowerCase().includes(nameVal);
      const matchesDept = !deptVal || doc.department === deptVal;
      const matchesRole = !roleVal || doc.role === roleVal;
      return matchesName && matchesDept && matchesRole;
    });
    renderDoctors(filtered);
  }

  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    renderDoctors(doctors);
    
    // Ті самі слухачі подій
    document.getElementById('nameSearch').addEventListener('input', handleFilters);
    document.getElementById('deptFilter').addEventListener('change', handleFilters);
    document.getElementById('roleFilter').addEventListener('change', handleFilters);

    // Логіка для виїзної панелі на мобільних
    const toggleBtn = document.getElementById('toggleFilters');
    const filterPanel = document.getElementById('filterPanel');
    toggleBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      filterPanel.classList.toggle('hidden');
      filterPanel.classList.toggle('animate-fade-down'); // Можна додати анімацію
    });
  });
</script>